I"¢<h2 id="some-basics">some basics</h2>

<h3 id="create-app">create app</h3>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>npx create-react-app <span class="nb">.</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>create a react app in the current directory</p>

<h3 id="run-server">run server</h3>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>npm start
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>run server on localhost:3000</p>

<h3 id="simple-app">simple app</h3>
<p>in src remove everything except :</p>
<ul>
  <li>App.css</li>
  <li>App.js</li>
  <li>index.js</li>
</ul>

<p>and there import on index.js</p>

<h3 id="how-it-work">how it work</h3>

<p>everything will go into <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;div id='root'&gt;</code> when the page is loaded. No need to reload again.</p>

<p>pro : nothing need to be download</p>

